# SupportInsight

Main Components:

## Setup Server

- Create .env in server directory, and put:

  # MongoDB Configuration

  MONGO_URI={mongo_uri}
  MONGO_DB={db_name}

  # Server Configuration

- python -m venv venv
- Run venv
  - venv\Scripts\activate (Windows)
- pip install -r requirements.txt

## Run Python Server

- cd server
- Run venv
  - venv\Scripts\activate (Windows)
- uvicorn main:app